data.description: Buyer credit $2000!  Look NO Stairs!  This is the only active ground level condo in the complex with one step at the entry. A prime location with quick access to the mountains, Chatfield Resevoir and all shopping near Southwest Plaza as well as foodie fun! You are minutes from 470 to take you up I-70 or just stay on 285.  The shopping includes all the big box stores and restraunts galore!  This cozy condo offers an open concept living, dining, kitchen area with two bedrooms and completely update beautiful bathroom.  A fenced in dog area, summer pool and walkable neighborhood.  Must see to appreciate.  Available for quick close and possession!
